Program: Outlook
Title: Pressures of Caste on Indian Families
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrsn
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The caste system in India and pressures that can lead parents to kill their own children. Also, Golden Kids News, a radio programme by former child soldiers in Sierra Leone; the benefits of dimming the streetlights in Calgary, Canada. Presenter: Reeta Chakrabarti.